        "timestamp_ms": 1773297902010,
        "text": "India I love you.\n\nOne thing is very clear.\n\nThe consumption wave is just beginning.\n\nHundreds of millions of people are moving into the middle class.\n\nSmartphone penetration continues to rise.\n\nDigital payments are everywhere.\n\nAnd a new generation of founders are building companies from this massive shift.\n\nRight now everyone is focused on AI \n\nAnd they should be.\n\nAI will power a lot of of the next generation of businesses.\n\nBut one of the biggest opportunities in tech over the next decade isn’t just AI.\n\nIt’s India.\n\nThe scale of the consumer market that’s forming there is unlike anything we’ve seen in decades.\n\nWe’re still early.\n\n🇮🇳🚀",
