        "posted_at": "2026-01-27 18:04:56",
        "timestamp_ms": 1769533496588,
        "text": "India and Europe just reset global trade.\n\nThis is will change India forever.\n\nIndia and the European Union just signed a massive retrade agreement.\n\nCreating one of the largest free trade zones in the world.\n\nThis matters.\n\nCovers over 2 billion people.\n\nRepresents 25% of global GDP.\n\nThe trade between India and Europe is already over 130B+ and will accelerate.\n\nIndia will now lower very high import taxes on European products.\n\nCars\nAuto Parts\nChemicals\nmachinery \n\nEurope will make it easier for Indian companies to sell there.\n\nTextiles & Garmets\nPharma\nGems and Jewelry \nElectronics \n\nBuild in India \n\nSell easily in Europe.\n\nIndia isn’t just a domestic market.\n\nIt’s becoming a global manufacturing export base.\n\n🇮🇳🚀",
