        "timestamp_ms": 1769189717867,
        "text": "India’s fintech infrastructure is exploding.\n\nJuspay just became India’s first unicorn of 2026.\n\nRaising $50M from my friends at WestBridge Capital at $1.2B valuation.\n\nIndia has leapfrogged many markets with digital payments.\n\nBut here’s the truth.\n\nAll of the front end apps got all the shine \n\nWhile the plumbing (infrastructure) was still fragile.\n\nThat’s where JUSPAY plays a massive role.\n\nMost digital payments in India move ridiculously fast.\n\nMerchant onboarding is complex.\n\nRisk & reconciliation are manual.\n\nCompanies like Swiggy and Flipkart don’t want another SDK. \n\nThey want robust payments orchestration that works.\n\nNow Juspay has crossed an annualised total payment volume of $1tn\n\nCongrats Sheetal Lalwani and Vimal Kumar \n\nThis is just the beginning!\n\n🇮🇳🚀",
