        "timestamp_ms": 1769101035826,
        "text": "India’s quick commerce has forever changed India.\n\nCreating a whole new habit for Indian consumers.\n\nHistorically speed has been everything.\n\nWhich has set the foundation.\n\nHowever quality got left behind.\n\nThat’s where FirstClub fills in the gap.\n\nBetting on a quality first quick commerce.\n\nCurated groceries, fresh produce, premium pantry staples.\n\nWhat I am seeing in the market is often low quality product offerings. \n\nIn a world where in the Indian consumer is getting way more health conscious.\n\nSince launching Ayyappan R and team have been growing like crazy getting inside the kitchen of many Indian consumers repeating orders weekly.\n\nFirstClub isn’t just a new Q Comm app \n\nIt’s a quality driven approach to convenience commerce.\n\nResonating with Indians who care about what’s inside there basket. \n\nNot just how quickly it can arrive. \n\nCheckout out the full podcast with Ayyappan as we go inside on what the future of FirstClub will be.\n\nLink to the full episode in the first comment below.\n\n🇮🇳🚀",
