        "text": "Indian founders building for India. \n\nIndian founders building for the globe.\n\nDifferent markets.\n\nSame ambition.\n\nThe next generation of category defining companies will be built by Indian founders.\n\nRidiculously technical \n\nRidiculously shameless \n\nRidiculously hungry \n\nI’m seeing it first hand sitting in Third Wave in HSR \n\nAnd sitting in Philz in Soma. \n\nThis isn’t a bubble \n\nThis is a India building for India and the world.\n\n🇮🇳🚀",
