        "url": "https://www.linkedin.com/posts/brendanprogers_indian-founders-want-access-to-silicon-valley-activity-7418704642651435008-mJ2i?utm_source=social_share_send&utm_medium=member_desktop_web&rcm=ACoAAGQeuYQB0hqkkjmCITWTdhpZY0vP6FqfhG8",
        "post_type": "repost",
        "posted_at": "2026-01-18 18:26:42",
        "timestamp_ms": 1768757202486,
        "text": "Indian founders want access to Silicon Valley.\n\nSilicon Valley is dying to get access to India.\n\nIndian founders want access to Silicon Valley from day one.\n\nBefore customers\n\nBefore hiring \n\nBefore going live\n\nThe issue is Indian founders are so early in there journey \n\nmost are not networked or have the right playbook to get into Silicon Valley.\n\n99% of Silicon Valley has zero idea to what look for nor want to go through the mud \n\nTo find to the next Zepto. \n\nThis creates a massive gap.\n\nThe secret? \n\nUnderstand the .001% Indian founder\n\nSource the heck out of that profile.\n\nBuild deep relationships with Silicon Valley funds who can provide value not just money to these founders.\n\nRinse and repeat.\n\nI am going all in on backing exceptional young Indian founders for the next 30 years.\n\nIndia X Silicon Valley \n\n🇮🇳🇺🇸🚀",
