        "url": "https://www.linkedin.com/posts/brendanprogers_44000-startups-launched-in-india-in-2025-activity-7417980225801826306-p35a?utm_source=social_share_send&utm_medium=member_desktop_web&rcm=ACoAAGQeuYQB0hqkkjmCITWTdhpZY0vP6FqfhG8",
