        "posted_at": "2026-01-16 18:25:45",
        "timestamp_ms": 1768584345078,
        "text": "44,000 startups launched in India in 2025.\n\nThe next decade for India is very clear.\n\nIn 2014 building a startup in India was called “niche”\n\nCapital was scarce \n\nTaking risk was looked down upon\n\nMost all companies were service or outsourcing led.\n\nIn 2025 \n\n44,000 new stsrtups were formed in India the highest ever.\n\nWhich makes India the 3rd largest startup ecosystem globally.\n\n50% of these startups are in tier2 tier3 cities \n\n45% women leadership \n\nFounders building for India and for the world.\n\nThis didn’t happen by accident \n\nIndian founders have put in the work \n\nThe next 25 years in India will change the world.\n\nI am Silicon Valley’s eyes and ears for early stage India.\n\nIf your an Indian founder in india or the US. \n\nI want to meet you. \n\nThis is just the beginning. \n\n🇮🇳🚀",
