        "text": "India is going through a transformational decade\n\nIndian founders are building for India and the world\n\nBeing in the Bay Area has given me the chance to meet other true believers in that journey. \n\nSpending time with Mohanjit Jolly partner at Ironpillar truly reinforced that conviction.\n\nWe talked about India’s next chapter\n\nHow enduring VC platforms scle \n\nAnd why the strongest founders are thinking globally from one.\n\nThis is just the beginning!\n\nGo India \n\n🇮🇳🚀",
