        "timestamp_ms": 1766415945824,
        "text": "India crypto moment is exploding.\n\nGen Z Indian’s are defying this moment\n\nIndia isn’t just adopting crypto anymore.\n\nFor millions of young Indian’s\n\nIt’s becoming a daily habit \n\nTo invest , learn , experiment and build.\n\nNo one understands this better than \n\nSumit Gupta Co-Founder, CEO of CoinDCX \n\nWhen we sat down with Sumit, he didn’t talk hype .\n\nHe talked exactly what’s happening on the ground.\n\nThe surge of Gen Z users entering Web3 every day.\n\nHow crypto in India is evolving into real utility and infrastructure.\n\nWhy regulatory clarity will accelerate innovation\n\nAnd the mindset required to build through cycles.\n\nThis is the beginning of a new financial operating system for India’s youth!\n\nCheck out our second episode of our podcast “The Making of An Indian Entrepreneur” \n\nLink in the first comment below.\n\n🚀🇮🇳",
