        "timestamp_ms": 1775728438712,
        "text": "Truth: AI is advancing at a crazy speed. Everyday we wake up to new definitions of what's possible. \n\nQuestion: How do you keep up exponential growth, and think about safety & future possibilities...all at the same time? \n\nChatted about this and a lot more, with Anthropic CTO Rahul Patil, at South Park Commons, Bangalore. \n\nFull episode is out now! Link in comments.",
