        "url": "https://www.linkedin.com/posts/activity-7447568179763056640-yjmd?utm_source=social_share_send&utm_medium=member_desktop_web&rcm=ACoAAGbYilkBsT-7xuT6Ux9P0MMOzZMgTeRaYDw",
        "post_type": "repost",
        "posted_at": "2026-04-08 16:11:56",
        "timestamp_ms": 1775657516216,
        "text": "Claude Mythos just scored 94% on the SWE-bench. The pace at which AI is eating software is unreal.\n\nAt South Park Commons, we think a lot about technology being in the Eye of Sauron. Today that Eye got a lot sharper.\n\nBut you can't prompt your way to a rocket engine. No model is getting defense certification or fabricating a chip (anytime soon, at least). The founders building in space, defense, drones, and deep tech hardware are playing a different game entirely.\n\nWe're getting them in one room. Escape Velocity — an evening at South Park Commons, Bangalore. India's space and defense tech builders, live demos, and a lot of nerding out over things that fly, launch, and shoot.\n\nIf you're building here or just curious — apply to demo. Link in comments.",
