        "text": "What does a product team look like when agents handle the mechanics?\n\nWe're sitting down with Tom Moor (Linear), Thomas Paul Mann (Raycast) & Michael Cohen (Anthropic) to find out.\n\nApril 30, 6–8PM @ South Park Commons NYC\n\nRSVP → https://luma.com/ldp71ob2",
