        "post_type": "repost",
        "posted_at": "2026-04-06 20:53:52",
        "timestamp_ms": 1775501632668,
        "text": "AI is rewriting the rules of security. How do you build defenses at machine speed?\n\nThe only way to defend against AI threats is with AI.\n\nNikesh Arora, CEO of the world's largest cybersecurity company Palo Alto Networks, is joining us at South Park Commons on April 20th.\n\nRSVP https://lnkd.in/gyQCUEhP",
