        "timestamp_ms": 1775052257942,
        "text": "Real, working demos are hard. Making them excellent, is harder. At South Park Commons India, doing hard things...is the thing! And that was the brief for our second ever Demo Faire in India.\n\nHere's a quick highlight of the evening, where SPC India portfolio companies continued to raise the bar!",
